but this guy's talking about being translated 1,500 feet or 1,500 yards, and one time he went 50 miles to a Waffle House.

00:56:07.741 --> 00:56:11.575
He's talking about it and President Trump's friends with him, and President Trump says he is serious.

00:56:11.576 --> 00:56:28.039
He's saying all this stuff and I'm thinking, 'This is pretty cool, I guess.'I mean, to me, it's on FEMA, it's on the news, and President Trump knows about it.

00:56:28.040 --> 00:56:38.399
So, I don't know. Kind of weird. All right. You want to take communion with me? So, this is another thing I want to say real quick.

00:56:38.400 --> 00:56:46.489
The video I told you all I saw, President Trump and they were using the NATO...

00:56:46.490 --> 00:56:58.774
No more videos. We got to hurry. How long have we been going? Probably way too long.

00:56:58.775 --> 00:57:07.359
55 minutes? It's too long. Well, this is my favorite part. The prayer parts work for me.

00:57:07.360 --> 00:57:16.129
Dipping in the river and pulling it—it's a lot. It makes me tired. I'm probably delaying. Sorry.

00:57:16.130 --> 00:57:28.919
But what I was going to tell you all, whenever I got through the last video, I want you to know my heart is for this country.

00:57:28.920 --> 00:57:43.980
My heart is for President Trump. My heart is to pray for this nation with everything I have that we make it to the finish line. We will not be a goat nation. We will remain a sheep nation.

00:57:43.981 --> 00:57:56.125
Anytime I'm telling you I'm seeing a warning to pray for President Trump's safety because of idolatry in the church, it's not me attacking.

00:57:56.126 --> 00:58:05.116
I'm trying to warn you to stop it, to look to Jesus, the author and the finisher of our faith, not looking at President Trump.

00:58:05.117 --> 00:58:13.541
Yes, President Trump has been a godsend, in my opinion, compared to the other people we've had in the past.

00:58:13.543 --> 00:58:24.014
Even when we thought George Bush was a good God-fearing man, compared to what I believe that we're seeing—at least him implement and help the Iranian people.

00:58:24.015 --> 00:58:27.705
And yeah, there are people that don't agree with any of this stuff.

00:58:27.706 --> 00:58:32.900
I told you it was Plan B concerning making America great again.

00:58:32.901 --> 00:58:39.199
But what the devil meant for bad through war, God can turn it around for good to liberate the people.

00:58:39.200 --> 00:58:50.512
I truly believe that, brothers and sisters, the 40,000 people that were martyred, mowed down by the Iranian government a couple of months ago—most people forget about that.

00:58:50.513 --> 00:58:58.759
As they were protesting, the Iranian government came out and just mowed them all down and massacred them.

00:58:58.760 --> 00:59:04.061
They showed the blood in the streets, and there was so much blood it looked like water.

00:59:04.062 --> 00:59:09.476
It was like a thick blood-water all throughout the streets. That's sickening for what I saw.

00:59:09.477 --> 00:59:12.257
People are trying to find their loved ones and they were just massacred.

00:59:12.258 --> 00:59:19.540
40,000 people from what I understand, but most people don't realize or care.

00:59:19.541 --> 00:59:28.039
They have short-term memory loss, you know. But we know all these things are happening.

00:59:28.040 --> 00:59:37.698
And I know what the Lord has told me, that a great revival is coming to the people of Iran and Cuba in the days ahead, that He's not done with it.

00:59:37.699 --> 00:59:51.319
There will be a great awakening, a great cry for souls in Iran, and we will see the underground church rise up with great miracles. Are we seeing that now? I don't know. I pray we are.

00:59:51.320 --> 01:00:22.159
But as I pray for President Trump, it's to make sure that he always keeps the main thing and he always keeps vertical—that he doesn't go horizontal and get prideful with the power that God's bestowed upon him to have the most powerful military in the world, to have whatever he needs at his fingertips, but to always keep vertical.

01:00:22.160 --> 01:00:38.776
Trump needs to keep vertical. And that's why I told you the Lord said, 'I will hold the church accountable for these blocks that are on his feet to get him across the finish line.'And how do we do that?

01:00:38.777 --> 01:00:46.759
By praying for him—that he doesn't go horizontal, that he doesn't start looking at himself as something that he's not, a God figure.

01:00:46.760 --> 01:00:50.031
He is not Jesus in the photo and everybody wants to defend it.

01:00:50.032 --> 01:00:56.159
'Brandon, you're wrong.'No, out of the heart. There's things there that the Lord said you don't know.

01:00:56.160 --> 01:01:09.559
And I'm not here as a prophetic voice, as a watchman to warn you; you are naive to what the Lord is telling me. A root of pride is trying to step in.

01:01:09.560 --> 01:01:14.462
And the only way you're ever going to get there, with Franklin Graham and all these people coming out and saying how great he is...

01:01:14.463 --> 01:01:19.039
I believe he's a great guy. Yeah, he has flesh. We all have flesh.

01:01:19.040 --> 01:01:24.439
But the Lord said to keep the main thing the main thing and always go vertical.

01:01:24.440 --> 01:01:28.453
Keep your eyes on Him. And what does that entail for the church?

01:01:28.454 --> 01:01:36.319
To keep ourselves on our knees that we pray for him. We don't idolize or worship.

01:01:36.320 --> 01:01:41.726
'Oh, Trump's the greatest! Trump, Trump, Trump!'No, Jesus is the greatest. Jesus, Jesus, Jesus.

01:01:41.727 --> 01:01:54.239
And we thank you, Lord, that we have a man after your own heart that will lead this nation—one nation under God.

01:01:54.240 --> 01:02:05.039
Under God, not under Trump. Under God. 'Well, Brandon, that's obvious.'No, it's not obvious to a lot of you. We get the emails.

01:02:05.040 --> 01:02:13.919
Regardless of Sister Clipboard out there going, 'Man, you're not talking to me.'Well, maybe not, keyboard warrior. I may not be talking to you, or maybe I am.

01:02:13.920 --> 01:02:19.916
But you need to get off your high horse and think about what I'm saying instead of typing away on your keyboard, always judging me.

01:02:19.918 --> 01:02:27.363
I'm trying to tell you, get on your face before a holy God and seek Him, and He will direct this path.

01:02:27.364 --> 01:02:31.296
He will direct Trump. He will do all that we need to do in the spirit realm.

01:02:31.297 --> 01:02:46.519
If we seek Jesus—'If my people who are called by my name will humble themselves and pray and turn from their wicked ways'—then who will heal our land?

01:02:46.520 --> 01:02:52.796
Jesus. He will fix it. He's the one that's going to fix all this.

01:02:52.797 --> 01:02:59.879
Will he use Trump to do it? If that's what he wants to do. He could use you.

01:02:59.880 --> 01:03:06.929
Doesn't mean he has to use Trump. He can use whoever says, 'I am here, Lord, use me.

01:03:06.930 --> 01:03:12.799
Send me.'Some plant, some water, but God always brings forth the increase.

01:03:12.800 --> 01:03:17.679
It's not you who brings it, and neither is it Trump. It's Jesus.

01:03:17.680 --> 01:03:21.648
He will bring forth the increase in these end times. Jesus will.

01:03:21.649 --> 01:03:29.305
He will bring forth the repentance. He will do this. But it's through the church praying and not exalting a man.

01:03:29.306 --> 01:03:44.736
He is not Caesar Augustus. He is not whatever. We always need to give Jesus all the praise, and He will change the heart of Pharaohs.

01:03:44.737 --> 01:03:52.639
He has the heart of the king; the Bible says the heart of the king is in the hand of the Lord.

01:03:52.640 --> 01:04:02.104
So we pray for Donald Trump. We lift up his family. We lift up his marriage. The Lord said specifically pray over his marriage.

01:04:02.105 --> 01:04:09.993
The Lord said specifically pray for the safety of his kids and his grandkids. That's our job.

01:04:09.994 --> 01:04:14.999
Would I love to meet him one day and give him a hug and say, 'Great job, you're a good guy, man'?

01:04:15.000 --> 01:04:18.100
Just give you a hug. Do I agree with everything that you've done? No.

01:04:18.101 --> 01:04:24.999
But it's a lot better than Bush, it's a lot better than Obama, and it's certainly better than the Clintons.

01:04:25.000 --> 01:04:34.039
So we just go, "Hey God, this is who we have in there."We pray for him to get across the finish line, but he is not a deity.

01:04:34.040 --> 01:04:38.799
Kim prophesied, Brandon. That's how many times Kim prophesied.

01:04:38.800 --> 01:04:48.033
I'm not rebutting what Kim Clement prophesied. I love Kim Clement. I love his family. I'm not rebutting that.

01:04:48.034 --> 01:05:02.439
I'm trying to tell you that regardless of what Kim Clement prophesied, it won't happen unless you pray him through it. Prophecy is free will.

01:05:02.440 --> 01:05:09.510
You can prophesy over me all day long and say, "Brandon, you're going to do this and you're going to do that."But it's my free will to do it.

01:05:09.511 --> 01:05:15.879
Prophecies don't force you to do something; you still have free will.

01:05:15.880 --> 01:05:21.087
And it's still our job as a church to pray for him. Regardless of Kim Clement, R.W.

01:05:21.088 --> 01:05:32.196
Schambach, or whoever prophesied, I don't care. As I said, we all can miss it. As much as I love Kim Clement, I'm sure he can miss it.

01:05:32.197 --> 01:05:39.143
And if he was here today, he'd probably tell you the same thing: "Hey, I missed it before."Have I missed it before?

01:05:39.144 --> 01:05:44.190
Is he a deity? No. He's a man just like Brandon Biggs. He's a man just like anybody else.

01:05:44.191 --> 01:05:50.759
Can Kim Clement miss it? I'm sure he could. Do I know that he has? I don't.

01:05:50.760 --> 01:05:59.599
I told his daughter, "I believe he's one of the most accurate prophets of this generation."And I still stand by that.

01:05:59.600 --> 01:06:05.435
Now, do we always try to make his words fit when we think they should fit?

01:06:05.436 --> 01:06:12.799
Yeah, people do. He's not here to defend himself; the Lord took him home. He's gone.

01:06:12.800 --> 01:06:26.239
But where one general goes home, God raises up a new one and says, "Finish the race."And if that general goes home, God will raise up another one and say, "Finish the race.

01:06:26.240 --> 01:06:38.119
Run."It doesn't mean the job's done. When a major soldier dies on the battlefield, God brings up another soldier to grab the gun and keep going.

01:06:38.120 --> 01:06:41.688
And that's what we're seeing with this generation. He went home in 2015.

01:06:41.689 --> 01:06:54.239
God's raising up new voices. And that's what happens; it's called the cycle of life. So, we don't idolize people.

01:06:54.240 --> 01:07:00.638
The moment you start idolizing people instead of the Lord Jesus Christ, you're on the wrong road.

01:07:00.639 --> 01:07:06.987
I have to correct that a little bit tonight. There are so many of you who are on the wrong road.

01:07:06.988 --> 01:07:21.619
Look to Jesus. Stop idolizing prophetic voices. Stop idolizing ministers, presidents, and celebrities because man will let you down.

01:07:21.620 --> 01:07:28.399
Jesus will never let you down. Man will fail you; Jesus will never fail you.

01:07:28.400 --> 01:07:36.433
He's perfect and he loves you and he gave his life for you. And the moment we keep the main thing, we'll always be victorious.

01:07:36.434 --> 01:07:43.319
But if we get off and start getting weird, guess what? Correction will come.

01:07:43.320 --> 01:07:54.474
We have to keep our eyes on Jesus in these last days because many will see all these weird doctrines, doctrines of demons.

01:07:54.475 --> 01:08:05.959
Men will be swayed by doctrines of demons, and the Bible warned us it was coming. Many false prophets will rise.

01:08:05.960 --> 01:08:16.259
Don't allow yourself to be snared by false prophetic words and false teachings just because you see something.

01:08:16.260 --> 01:08:22.608
I told you they're going to perform miracles in the days ahead. They're going to raise the dead in the days ahead.

01:08:22.609 --> 01:08:32.318
And just because you see them perform a miracle and see signs and wonders in their ministry doesn't mean they're of God.

01:08:32.319 --> 01:08:39.262
You're going to have to know and have great discernment. Just because they walk in the supernatural...

01:08:39.263 --> 01:08:48.318
think about this: Pharaoh's men doing miracles and demonic stuff with their staffs and the snakes.

01:08:48.319 --> 01:08:58.719
They threw them down and Moses's snake ate theirs, but it didn't mean they couldn't perform the same kind of stuff, black magic, and the things they were doing.

01:08:58.720 --> 01:09:07.907
So be careful who you follow. Just because you see them do something, discern it.

01:09:07.908 --> 01:09:17.519
Be vigilant to filter in these last days because we're going to be snared if you don't.

01:09:17.520 --> 01:09:25.479
I don't care what they say. I don't care what they do. Always stay vertical and keep your eyes on Jesus.

01:09:25.480 --> 01:09:32.919
Keep him the main thing in these last days. If you don't, you're in trouble.

01:09:32.920 --> 01:09:39.776
We must keep Jesus first. And the Bible—back it up with the word.

01:09:39.777 --> 01:09:45.479
Read the word. Read it and read it some more. And the more you read it, the more you're going to know.

01:09:45.480 --> 01:09:49.399
The Bible says you'll know the truth and the truth will set you free.

01:09:49.400 --> 01:09:55.390
So we can't be following prophetic so-and-so all the time and saying, "That's it right there.

01:09:55.391 --> 01:09:59.573
That's set in stone."Find it. Read the word. Keep your eyes on him.

01:09:59.574 --> 01:10:08.274
If it witnesses with you in your spirit that we're in the last days, then fine, keep running with it.

01:10:08.275 --> 01:10:19.879
If not, judge it. Keep quiet and just be still. Don't be so quick to jump on AI and all these things that we're about to see—many things to snare us.

01:10:19.880 --> 01:10:29.600
I hope that helps you because I feel like there's so much idolizing and weirdness.

01:10:29.601 --> 01:10:38.643
"Erica said this, she has the blue eyes, she's Esther."I don't know if she's Esther; the Lord didn't give me that word.

01:10:38.644 --> 01:10:46.799
You can't ask him because he went home. All we know is we have a recording of him saying something.

01:10:46.800 --> 01:10:59.763
You have to just weigh things out and pray about it. It's healthy to really test the spirits, to sit there and listen.

01:10:59.764 --> 01:11:09.879
I didn't say be a sister with your clipboard and be mean; I said test in your own spirit and see if it witnesses with you.

01:11:09.880 --> 01:11:14.891
Is the Holy Spirit speaking this to me? Because I hear him just like that man can.

01:11:14.892 --> 01:11:32.236
I may not walk in the gifting of a prophet or a watcher, but I know that He said, "My sheep will know my voice and a stranger's voice I will not follow."And those who are led by the spirit of God are the sons and the daughters of God.

01:11:32.237 --> 01:11:39.127
He didn't say be led by prophets; be led by the spirit of God in these last days.

01:11:39.128 --> 01:11:46.399
You must keep the main thing the main thing: Jesus. Vertical.

01:11:46.400 --> 01:11:53.890
I'm looking at you. Not all this stuff down here. There's too much static, too much noise.

01:11:53.891 --> 01:11:59.792
I'm keeping my eyes on you. Crack this Bible open. Read it. Take communion.

01:11:59.793 --> 01:12:08.598
Pray in the Holy Ghost. Sing songs. Whatever you have to do, but you've got to hear him for yourself.

01:12:08.599 --> 01:12:12.755
I'm telling you, I see a storm coming. Now, if that witnesses with you, fine.

01:12:12.756 --> 01:12:21.119
If you say, "Brandon, I feel like you missed it,"well, I'm human. I pray I didn't. I'm doing the best I can.

01:12:21.120 --> 01:12:30.959
But please don't use anything that I say and go, "Hey, we're taking you by the word, Brandon."That's foolish.

01:12:30.960 --> 01:12:35.999
Always judge the words even that I give and say, "Listen, I don't feel right."Okay.

01:12:36.000 --> 01:12:41.370
I tell Sister Billye that all the time. If I'm wrong, rebuke me.

01:12:41.371 --> 01:12:48.077
Tell me I'm wrong, I'm false, and I need to get right. I am never above correction from my elders.

01:12:48.078 --> 01:12:55.603
I always tell them—from Billy Burke to Billye Brim to whoever—if you feel it's off, rebuke me and tell me.

01:12:55.604 --> 01:13:00.026
I am your elder, and I feel you're off and you need to be corrected.

01:13:00.027 --> 01:13:03.408
I listen. Give me a spiritual spanking through the Holy Ghost.

01:13:03.409 --> 01:13:13.257
I'm not above correction, but I am against the keyboard warriors in the comment section thinking they have spiritual stuff when you don't even know the difference between the Holy Ghost or whatever.

01:13:13.258 --> 01:13:27.235
I'm talking about people who are mature in the word of God, not people who have just been born again for two weeks and think they can correct you.

01:13:27.236 --> 01:13:35.159
No, no, no. I'll listen to the elders, but I'm not listening to such a keyboard warrior on there. Be still.

01:13:35.160 --> 01:13:49.586
You wouldn't know the Holy Ghost if he walked in and had HG on his head on a hat, Holy Ghost choir and angels behind you, and you're going, 'I wonder if that's the Lord.'I'm like, 'Yes, it's the Lord.'Just saying.

01:13:49.587 --> 01:13:54.359
Not trying to be rude, but there's a lot of you that are very immature.

01:13:54.360 --> 01:14:05.758
So, I say that all in love and I try to help as much as I can. And if you love me, you love me. If you don't, you don't.

01:14:05.759 --> 01:14:09.479
Lord said, 'Man, there's going to be a lot of people that hate you.'And I said, 'Well, okay, that's right.

01:14:09.480 --> 01:14:15.519
I stand with you and we do the best we can with what we give him, Lord.

01:14:15.520 --> 01:14:21.359
We seek you and we will find you.'And my job is always to point you to Jesus.

01:14:21.360 --> 01:14:29.119
You must know him. You must have a relationship with him. You're running out of time.

01:14:29.120 --> 01:14:36.119
I truly believe as we see the signs of the times all around us, you must know him.

01:14:36.120 --> 01:14:44.079
You must have a revelation of who he is. My sheep. Are you his? Do you belong to him?

01:14:44.080 --> 01:14:49.559
There's many of you tonight that sit here and say, 'Brandon, I don't know him.

01:14:49.560 --> 01:14:56.699
If I die tonight, where would I spend eternity?'Unless a man is born again, he will not enter into the kingdom of God.

01:14:56.700 --> 01:15:05.875
That's what my Bible says. So, you must know Jesus Christ. I'm going to ask you just real quick, do you know my friend?

01:15:05.876 --> 01:15:16.949
Before we go on, and you may say, 'I don't know him.'But I want to pray for you because tonight might be your last opportunity as those eight children went home to be with the Lord.

01:15:16.950 --> 01:15:22.025
There's so many people. There's perilous times all around us. And none of us are promised tomorrow.

01:15:22.026 --> 01:15:29.478
The very shoes you put on today to go to work, the very shoes you put on, the undertaker might be taking off that evening.

01:15:29.479 --> 01:15:37.286
You need to know there's a heaven to gain and a hell to shun. And you need to know that Jesus Christ is the only way to the Father.

01:15:37.287 --> 01:15:43.349
Muhammad won't get you there. Buddha won't get you there. No satanic principality is going to get you there.

01:15:43.350 --> 01:15:55.634
The only way to the Father is through the Lord Jesus Christ. And tonight you have an opportunity to accept him as your Lord and Savior. I want to pray for you and just say a simple prayer right now.

01:15:55.635 --> 01:16:11.936
And all you have to do is accept Jesus Christ right now and repent and turn from your sins and say, 'Jesus, I make you my Lord and personal Savior tonight.'If I'm talking to you and you're watching this right now and you say, 'Brandon, after the first half, you shook me a little bit.

01:16:11.937 --> 01:16:15.367
I know I'm not living right. I've been living in sin. I've been going to the clubs.

01:16:15.368 --> 01:16:18.493
I've been doing things that I know that I shouldn't be doing.

01:16:18.494 --> 01:16:21.753
But tonight, I want to make things right. Tonight, I'm coming home.

01:16:21.754 --> 01:16:29.799
Will you please pray for me?'I would love to. But you've got to get real with God.

01:16:29.800 --> 01:16:37.399
And God's got to get real with you. The moment you get real with God, God will become real to you.

01:16:37.400 --> 01:16:40.796
So, I'm going to say a simple prayer, but I want you to be bold in your decision tonight.

01:16:40.797 --> 01:16:48.183
And I want you to say in the comment section tonight, 'Tonight's my night. I want to be saved. Tonight's my night.

01:16:48.184 --> 01:16:58.190
I'm coming home.'You may have been a person who was radically on fire for Jesus at one point in time in your life, but over the course of time, you've leaked out.

01:16:58.191 --> 01:17:02.080
You're not as full. You're not excited about Christianity anymore.

01:17:02.081 --> 01:17:10.999
You went back to the vomit that you repented over in the first place and said, 'Lord, I don't want to be a part of this anymore.'And now you're back doing it.

01:17:11.000 --> 01:17:15.782
But tonight, you have an opportunity to sell out to Jesus. You're like the prodigal.

01:17:15.783 --> 01:17:22.479
Run to the Father when you sin. Don't run away from him. So, I'm going to say this simple prayer and I want you to repeat it after me.

01:17:22.480 --> 01:17:31.199
Say, 'Jesus, I believe you are the Son of God. I believe you died for me and you rose again on the third day.

01:17:31.200 --> 01:17:39.159
I believe you're making intercession for me right now. Jesus, I'm a sinner and I need a savior.

01:17:39.160 --> 01:17:49.119
I repent of my sins. I ask you to forgive me for all I've done. As of tonight, Lord, I turn my back on the sin.

01:17:49.120 --> 01:17:56.999
I turn my back on the devil. I turn my back on any kind of agreement I've made with the devil.

01:17:57.000 --> 01:18:06.679
And from this day forward, I'm sold out to you. Jesus, I ask you to write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

01:18:06.680 --> 01:18:11.899
Jesus, I ask you to invade my life. Create in me a clean heart.

01:18:11.900 --> 01:18:18.242
Wash me with your precious blood. I do believe you are the Son of God.

01:18:18.243 --> 01:18:24.839
And I do believe that you rose again on the third day. Jesus, I love you.

01:18:24.840 --> 01:18:32.239
I dedicate my life to you. From this day forward, Lord, I'm sold out to you.

01:18:32.240 --> 01:18:39.279
If I die tonight, Lord, I know I'll be with you in paradise forever.

01:18:39.280 --> 01:18:45.754
Amen and amen.'If you just said that prayer, I believe you just gave your heart to Jesus Christ and you're born again.

01:18:45.755 --> 01:18:52.119
Now, what do you do? Go to a Bible-believing church. I'd go to one that teaches the word.

01:18:52.120 --> 01:18:55.576
I'd go to non-denominational. That's where we would go. My wife and I would go.

01:18:55.577 --> 01:19:04.479
You go where you feel like you're getting fed. But either way, you must grow spiritually and find a church that feeds you.

01:19:04.480 --> 01:19:13.439
Tell the pastor there, say, 'Listen, I want to be water baptized.'I would go to a church also that speaks in tongues.

01:19:13.440 --> 01:19:15.801
There's a lot of good churches like Church of His Presence down south.

01:19:15.802 --> 01:19:20.799
If you live down south, the Church of His Presence. There's Glorious Church in Collinsville, Oklahoma.

01:19:20.800 --> 01:19:27.675
There's all kinds of good churches that are around that will teach you the word of God, that will teach you how to get baptized in the Holy Ghost.

01:19:27.676 --> 01:19:30.494
Why Tongues? by Kenneth E. E. Hagin. There's so many good churches.

01:19:30.495 --> 01:19:37.413
There's a church, Harvest Church in Tennessee, from what I understand. That lady there, Billy Burke, goes, and that's amazing.

