02:19:32.160 --> 02:19:40.558
But I refuse to be moved by what I see and who is involved in this. And that's all I will say.

02:19:40.559 --> 02:19:44.944
If you're a praying Christian, you better pray over our president.

02:19:44.945 --> 02:19:53.239
Pray over these heads of government and pray for their wisdom. They need wisdom right now.

02:19:53.240 --> 02:20:07.697
There is too much distraction—the Pope arguing and all this stuff—it's just distractions. Put away the cell phones. This is like DEFCON 5.

02:20:07.698 --> 02:20:23.399
Praying over midterms going into the summer—May, June, July, August, September, and we are there in October for the midterms, six months away.

02:20:23.400 --> 02:20:33.470
Praying over our leadership and these very important Senate and House seats or governor races.

02:20:33.471 --> 02:20:49.319
This is vital to America for the next two years, and this is such a vital time to finish his term out strong.

02:20:49.320 --> 02:20:58.959
I would say political theater and embarrassing moments are just about popular opinion.

02:20:58.960 --> 02:21:22.679
Remember this, I saw the media—CNN, Fox, MSNBC—losing control, and it was the Rockefellers and the deep state.

02:21:22.680 --> 02:21:31.992
This is about media because if they lose the media, they lose influence.

02:21:31.993 --> 02:21:41.698
The influence of what people watch is turning to alternative media like Alex Jones and Glenn Beck.

02:21:41.699 --> 02:21:57.279
You have to get a stronghold in alternative media. Because as this media loses control, alternative media will be the source. So you've got to get a foothold in alternative.

02:21:57.280 --> 02:22:20.119
And then you try to switch it back to the ones that were your puppets before, because when the people's eyes are watching, it's influence on their minds, and they get the votes and the way the whole thing goes, right?

02:22:20.120 --> 02:22:27.217
Through COVID, through all these 9/11 things, right? You see how it all happens.

02:22:27.218 --> 02:22:32.895
It's all puppeteers. How does the puppet manipulate the thing?

02:22:32.896 --> 02:22:39.795
And that's what I'm trying to tell you all. There's very dark things afoot in the days ahead.

02:22:39.796 --> 02:22:48.839
And you must pray for President Trump's protection over his cabinet. A house divided cannot stand.

02:22:48.840 --> 02:23:00.295
Strife and every work with social media, the tweets, and all the X posts and all the crap is distraction from this.

02:23:00.296 --> 02:23:12.217
And so you see alien files, things like that. It comes out. But the main thing is to keep the masses distracted.

02:23:12.218 --> 02:23:26.759
But it's bigger than that. There's something very dark. We don't want to lose our nation.

02:23:26.760 --> 02:23:33.679
And the only way we're going to stop this is by true intercessory prayer.

02:23:33.680 --> 02:23:45.519
And even what the Lord said to me, he said, 'Brandon, there'll be some of this that we will...'I heard him and there's things I'm hearing. He said, 'Some of this you will not stop.

02:23:45.520 --> 02:23:56.554
This is to accelerate you into the birthing pains for the end times.'But it doesn't mean that you won't be protected and that it won't have nothing to do with you.

02:23:56.555 --> 02:24:08.359
You can say, 'Hey, I'm going to be underneath the shelter of the Most High, the cleft of the rock.'Does that make sense?

02:24:08.360 --> 02:24:14.519
You may see it around you, but you can choose to look at this side.

02:24:14.520 --> 02:24:18.719
You can't stop everything, but you can choose to look at this side.

02:24:18.720 --> 02:24:23.999
Does that make sense? It's that thin. What you're about to see is this: thin.

02:24:24.000 --> 02:24:30.565
You can focus on the glory. Focus on the outpouring. What's your job of bringing in the harvest?

02:24:30.566 --> 02:24:36.209
No matter what, this side is getting really dark. You can choose to focus on this side, ladies and gentlemen.

02:24:36.210 --> 02:24:45.079
And that's what I'm trying to tell you. We may not stop this side, but we can focus on the glory and what part we play, right?

02:24:45.080 --> 02:24:47.845
We're going to lay hands on the sick. We're going to see them recover.

02:24:47.846 --> 02:24:54.572
Our job is to bring in the harvest. We can't get distracted with this side. This side is going to pull really hard in the days ahead.

02:24:54.573 --> 02:25:03.599
I want you to hear me: this side, the dark side, is going to pull you really hard in the days ahead.

02:25:03.600 --> 02:25:13.368
You're going to have to have a choice. You either focus on this side or this side, but they're both there. And what I see and all that the Lord said, don't.

02:25:13.369 --> 02:25:25.719
It's going to pull you very hard to focus directly just on this side because it's always going to be in front of your face because of what you're looking at on your phone.

02:25:25.720 --> 02:25:30.839
It's always presented in front of you instead of focusing on this.

02:25:30.840 --> 02:25:36.759
This is going to distract you to pull you away from the glory.

02:25:36.760 --> 02:25:42.279
Just remember what I'm telling you. It's going to come on like a waterfall.

02:25:42.280 --> 02:25:49.199
I'm telling you, a waterfall is coming. A storm is coming. A major hurricane.

02:25:49.200 --> 02:25:52.479
And everybody's going to be... and you'll remember what I told you.

02:25:52.480 --> 02:25:57.359
Remember, mark it on your calendars when Brandon, the Holy Spirit told you.

02:25:57.360 --> 02:26:07.395
Don't get distracted with this other side. It's coming and it's going to shake you and you're going to be like...

02:26:07.396 --> 02:26:14.999
but it's your choice. It's that thin. It's that thin. Okay. I'll leave you with that tonight.

02:26:15.000 --> 02:26:21.414
God bless you all. We love you. Remember, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

02:26:21.415 --> 02:26:30.160
Jesus loves you and we love you. God bless you and we'll see you again tomorrow. Bye-bye.

